Nigerian rapper Chibuzor Nelson Azubuike, popularly called Phyno has released the visuals to “Ride For You”. This track is off his recently released third body of work “Deal With It” which was unveiled early in the month of September. Other feathers on Phyno’s cap include two solid albums, The Playmaker and No Guts No Glory. The Soularge-produced song features multiple award-winning artiste Davido, who surprisingly sings a part of his verse in Igbo. Ride For You video was directed by the Patrick Elis and Clarence Peters. Watch the video below and feel free to rate Davido’s fluency in Igbo: 